

 - a small gap exists at the bottom of the screen allowing light to escape.
	- turn the brightness up in a dark room to see if your pixel has this failure
	- appears to be an issue with glue application on the glass covering the LCD

 - playing 4K youtube videos eventially causes the screen to become covered with white and grey stripes. These persist between boots.

 - touching the trackpad causes the top left area of the keyboard to emit a high pitched buzzing
	- test in a relatively quiet area
	- independent of a/c adapter presense, volume, and brightness

